ArcGIS project:

Theme: WCF Service
Technologies: .NET and Silverlight

Purpose:

Client should be able to query the geo-database through the service.
The application should provide methods that:
* search in the different layers (Cities, Highways, States, Counties) by layer attributes
* make geo-spatial search for Cities in area, pointed by X and Y coordinates and a Buffer
* make geo-spatial search in layer by layer (Cities that is in bounds of some State)
